title: ArianeGroup to Receive €340M Per Year to Operate Ariane 6
summary:
Member states of the European Space Agency have committed to provide ArianeGroup with up to €340 million a year to operate Ariane 6. title: Dish Network CEO makes early exit
summary: Dish Network said its CEO Erik Carlson is resigning Nov. 12 ahead of the broadcaster’s merger with EchoStar, its sister company focused on providing broadband services from space, after posting a steep drop in satellite TV customers.
